Sample used as a IT ticket


[-User Request-]
   │ > this comes either via: e-mail, phonecall or through ticketing system
   ▼      > [1/5/2026] UAM in HP for 3W Customer Support AMS request through ticketing system
[Smart Intake Form]
   │  (Complete info) (problem description - near-end info [IP,S/N,MAC,Host,Subnet-Timestamps etc]
   |  > SharePoint Form or Google Forms 
   ▼     > [UAM] Provided with Request / Profile name/ Short description/ Screenshot of UAM category ID/Type]
[Auto-Routed Ticket]
   │
   ▼   > [UAM] Auto creation of ticket after completing form. [Case N avaialable]
[Tier 2]
   │  (30 min)
   |  > Concierge can decrease the elapsed time from 30 to 15 mins via using Teams chat to engage MCS
   ▼
[Fix Applied]
   │
   |  > Fix needs to be tested <-> engage with end-user may be required based on issue type.
   ▼
[Auto-Confirmation]
   │
   |  > Auto-confirmation can be enabled post three-strikes no reply is triggered
   |  > (trigger would be three e-mails out with no reply) / send automated e-mail from CDAX.
   ▼
[Closed]


